<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Ngaihmanh, vanmi authawng cu, &quot;Bawi hrinthar thangthat ko u, Leicung
 ah daihnak um seh, Pathian le mi an i rem, Miphun vialte hna dir u, Vanmi
 he hlasa ti u. Bethlehem ah Jesuh Khrih, Kan Khamhtu cu a chuak cang.
 Ngaihmanh! vanmi authawng cu, &quot;Bawi hrinthar thangthat ko u.&quot;

[V2]
 Vancungmi lak Siangpahrang, A zungzal a nung kan Bawi, A caan a tlin
 in a tum, Lengnu tak ah a rung lang. Vawlei mi bang kan Bawi nih, Mi kha
 khamh a kan duh ca. A thiangmi a rung tum cang, Jesuh kan Emmanuel,
 Ngaihmanh! vanmi authawng cu, &quot;Bawi hrinthar thangthat ko u.&quot;

[V3]
 Daihnak Bawi, kan Siangpahrang, Dinnak Bawi thangthat ko u, Ceunak,
 nunnak mi vialte, Pek awkah a rung tum cang. A sunparnak kaltak in,
 Thihnak in nunnak thar ah. Vawlei cung mi vialte ca Hrinnak kha a in kan
 Bawi, Ngaihmanh! vanmi authawng cu, &quot;Bawi hrinthar thangthat ko u.&quot;</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
<title>NGAIHMANH! VANMI AUTHAWNG CH84</title>
<hymn_number>84</hymn_number>
</song>